#include<stdio.h>

char *text = "";

#define MAX_PAT 4
char* pat[MAX_PAT] = {"cat", "dog", "bat", "vpl"};

#define QUEUE_SIZE 100

struct trie_node {
    int leaf;
    struct trie_node* child[26];
    char word[500];
    struct trie_node *suffix_link;
    struct trie_node *endword;
    struct trie_node *parent;
    char parent_char;
};

struct trie_node *root;

struct trie_node *queue[QUEUE_SIZE];
int enqueue_idx;
int dequeue_idx;

void enqueue(struct trie_node *node)
{
    queue[enqueue_idx++] = node;
}

struct trie_node *dequeue()
{
    if (dequeue_idx < enqueue_idx)
        return queue[dequeue_idx++];
    return NULL;
}

void build_trie(char *str)
{
    struct trie_node *temp = root;
    int s_len = strlen(str);
    for (int i = 0; i < s_len; i++) {
        char ch = str[i];
        if (temp->child[ch - 'a'] == NULL) {
            temp->child[ch - 'a'] = (struct trie_node *)malloc(sizeof(struct trie_node));
            for (int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
                temp->child[ch - 'a']->child[i] = NULL;
            }
            temp->child[ch - 'a']->parent_char = ch;
            temp->child[ch - 'a']->parent = temp;
            temp->child[ch - 'a']->leaf = 0;
            temp->child[ch - 'a']->suffix_link = NULL;
            temp->child[ch - 'a']->endword = NULL;
        }
        temp = temp->child[ch - 'a'];
    }

    temp->leaf = 1;
    strcpy(temp->word, str);
}

void create_suffix_links()
{
    enqueue(root);
    struct trie_node *temp = dequeue();
    
    while(temp != NULL) {
        for (int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
            if (temp->child[i] != NULL)
                enqueue(temp->child[i]);
        }
        if (temp == root) {
            //nothing to be done
        } else {
            if (temp->parent == root) {
                temp->suffix_link = root;
                if (temp->leaf == 1)
                    temp->endword = temp;
                else {
                    temp->endword = temp->suffix_link->endword;
                }
            } else {
                struct trie_node *parent_suff_link = temp->parent->suffix_link;
                char ch = temp->parent_char;
                while(true) {
                    if (parent_suff_link->child[ch - 'a'] != NULL) {
                        temp->suffix_link = parent_suff_link->child[ch - 'a'];
                        if (temp->leaf == 1)
                            temp->endword = temp;
                        else {
                            temp->endword = temp->suffix_link->endword;
                        }
                        break;
                    } else {
                        parent_suff_link = parent_suff_link->suffix_link;
                        if (parent_suff_link == root) {
                            temp->suffix_link = root;
                            if (temp->leaf == 1)
                                temp->endword = temp;
                            else {
                                temp->endword = temp->suffix_link->endword;
                            }
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        temp = dequeue();
    }
}

void search(char *text)
{
    int t_len = strlen(text);
    struct trie_node *temp = root;
    
    for (int i = 0; i < t_len; i++) {
        char ch = text[i];
        
        // while loop to traverse node
        while(true) {
            if (temp->child[ch - 'a'] != NULL) {
                temp = temp->child[ch - 'a'];
                break;
            }
            if (temp == root)
                break;
            temp = temp->suffix_link;
        }
        struct trie_node *temp1 = temp;

        // while loop to find all words ending with this character
        while(true) {
            temp1 = temp1->endword;
            if (temp1 == root)
                break;
            printf("found word = %s\n", temp1->word);
            temp1 = temp1->suffix_link;
        }
    }
}

int main(void) {
    root = (struct trie_node *)malloc(sizeof(struct trie_node));
    for (int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
        root->child[i] = NULL;
    }
    root->leaf = 0;
    root->suffix_link = root;
    root->endword = root;
    
    for (int i = 0; i < MAX_PAT; i++) {
        //printf("inserting %s\n", pat[i]);
        build_trie(pat[i]);
    }
    
    create_suffix_links();
    
    search(text);
    return 0;
}
